      <title>尼日利亚立法者考虑修改《中央银行法》</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/nigerian-lawmakers-seek-to-strip-central-bank-of-crucial-powers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚立法者正在考虑对管理中央银行的立法进行修改，成立一个委员会来协调货币和财政政策，这引发了人们对银行独立性可能产生的影响的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/nigerian-lawmakers-seek-to-strip-central-bank-of-crucial-powers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 12:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
